title: Netra Bhandari
text: I am a PhD student in the Environmental Informatics lab at Univeristy of Marbrug. I am currently working in two projects , Kilimanjaro Socio-Ecological Systems and RIPA2TAN. I deal mainly with spatio-temporal data analysis.
